CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, September 28, 1957, pg. A1, reads: "New Tipstaff - Shortly after he was sworn in as a tipstaff in Allegheny County Court, Curtis B. Haines, his wife, Gladys, and Judge Louis K. Kaufman exchanged pleasantries. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Judge Louis L. Kaufman shaking hands with Curtis B. Haines, with Gladys Haines standing beside him, after his swearing in as Allegheny County Court tipstaff, posed in county court assignment room 533
